---
title: Tortelloni Pasta Bar One recipe–endless ways to enjoy!
description: How do you make everyone happy at dinner? A DIY tortellini bar! You’ll set out tender cheese tortelloni with marinara and garlic cream sauces, plus roasted zucchini, toasted panko, truffle oil, parsley, and Parmesan so everyone can create their own perfect pasta plate. Order extra broccoli for more veggies, or penne pasta for a vegan version.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/668d4250012d858ae3811d23-f55923be.jpeg
